{"tid":688190,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"拿小狗餵鱷龜　生物老師被起訴虐待動物罪","createTime":"2018-06-03T03:48:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-03T06:21:41.000Z","uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1775bc969daccb04812f41def7939b33884bb905","tid":688190,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T03:48:46.000Z","msg":"根據檢方調查，克羅斯蘭於今年3月放學後，在數名學生面前將一隻病懨懨的小狗餵食擬鱷龜。學生回家告知家長後讓此事曝光，網路上有將近19萬人連署，要求校方開除克羅斯蘭。「善待動物組織」（PETA）也發聲明譴責克羅斯蘭的行徑「兇殘，不應接近易遭影響的年輕人」。<br />\n不過網路上有也出現力挺克羅斯蘭的聲浪，發起「我們支持克羅斯蘭」網路連署的民眾表示，他是以嶄新的方式教授自然，且熱愛其工作。目前該連署約有3700人簽名支持，大部分是克羅斯蘭的同事、前學生及社區民眾。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180603/640_66b32e6f987fddaab0c2f7b52972e20e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180603%2F640_66b32e6f987fddaab0c2f7b52972e20e.jpg&h=4deb221d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁都告"},{"pid":"2792f18a6410f3513cb8edc64fccc267c4793de5","tid":688190,"uid":59511,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T03:57:37.000Z","msg":"如果係活雞/牛/羊就無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nI love animals.jpg"},{"pid":"501ced0857813a2adb84caac05d20ce30c725230","tid":688190,"uid":109983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T05:19:34.000Z","msg":"On9左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n狗肉先補啊"},{"pid":"7152a4fadf0019973d3a60b955a2d0afbb368669","tid":688190,"uid":173397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T05:22:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7bf1dcdcd1fd90649a2f0fa196859bc643fe7bab","tid":688190,"uid":41317,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T05:23:06.000Z","msg":"人都唔俾食狗, 何況你隻臭龜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <im